rows.label: tlk43200144_04_msg0001
rows.name:
The Great Stairway behind the
Holy Gate is cool, but so are the stairs
that lead downwards from the Plaza!

rows.label: tlk43200144_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I hear they lead to a place called the
Ruins of Fountain Park. Ah, but I don't
think I could make it all the way...

rows.label: tlk43200144_04_msg0003
rows.name:
You might be able to, if you could
jump a really long way... But for me,
it'd spell broken bones for sure!
